file.name: swagger.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
    title: ZED
    version: 1.0.1
servers:
    - url: "http://localhost:8000/"
components:
    securitySchemes:
      token:
        type: http
        scheme: bearer
        bearerFormat: JWT
paths:
  # Test
  /welcome:
    get:
      security:
        - token: []
      tags:
        - Test
      summary: Welcome
      description: Getting Started.
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Success.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  status:
                    type: string
                    example: "Success"
                  data:
                    type: string
                    example: "Welcome to ZED framework."
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 200
        "401":
          description: Unauthorized
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  status:
                    type: string
                    example: "Error"
                  data:
                    type: string
                    example: "Unauthorized"
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 401
    
  # Authentication
  /user/login:
    get:
      tags:
        - Authentication
      summary: Login
      description: Logging User In.
      responses:
          "200":
              description: Success.
              content:
                  application/json:
                      schema:
                          type: object
                          properties:
                              status:
                                  type: string
                                  example: "Success"
                              data:
                                  type: object
                                  properties:
                                      User:
                                          type: object
                                          properties:
                                              id:
                                                  type: integer
                                                  example: 1
                                              name:
                                                  type: string
                                                  example: "first-name"
                                              family:
                                                  type: string
                                                  example: "last-name"
                                              email:
                                                  type: string
                                                  example: "hitrav@info.com"
                                              birth_date:
                                                  type: string
                                                  example: "1970-01-01"
                                              country_code:
                                                  type: integer
                                                  example: 98
                                              mobile_number:
                                                  type: integer
                                                  example: 9000000000
                                              gender_name:
                                                  type: string
                                                  example: "gender"
                                              language_name:
                                                  type: string
                                                  example: "language"
                                      _link:
                                          type: array
                                          items:
                                              type: object
                                              properties:
                                                  rel:
                                                      type: string
                                                      example: "link-rel"
                                                  type:
                                                      type: string
                                                      example: "link-type"
                                                  href:
                                                      type: string
                                                      example: "url-route-to-profile"
                              code:
                                  type: integer
                                  example: 200
          "401":
              description: Unauthorized.
              content:
                  application/json:
                      schema:
                          type: object
                          properties:
                              status:
                                  type: string
                                  example: "Error"
                              data:
                                  type: string
                                  example: "Unauthorized"
                              code:
                                  type: integer
                                  example: 401
  /user/register:
    post:
      tags:
        - Authentication
      summary: Register
      description: Registering User.
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/x-www-form-urlencoded:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                name:
                  type: string
                surname:
                  type: string
                username:
                  type: string
                email:
                  type: string
                password:
                  type: string
                phone_number:
                  type: string
              required:
                - name
                - surname
                - username
                - email
                - password
                - phone_number
      responses:
        "200":
          description: User Registered Successfully.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  status:
                    type: string
                    example: "Success"
                  data:
                    type: string
                    example: "access-token"
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 200
